<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-MZ">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Baixar Finanças MZ</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b4aa, #ff7043);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 48px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease;
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #00695c;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .badge {
            background: #ff7043;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .features {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 24px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .features li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b4aa, #00897b);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        }
        .btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }
        .version {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="logo">💰</div>
        <h1>Finanças MZ</h1>
        <span class="badge">Versão 1.0</span>
        
        <ul class="features">
            <li>📱 M-Pesa + e-Mola</li>
            <li>💰 Calculadora de taxas oficiais 2026</li>
            <li>🛒 Lista de compras com preços</li>
            <li>✅ Gestão de tarefas</li>
            <li>🌙 Modo escuro/claro</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jacintoserafim117-del/Finan-as-MZ/main/FinancasMZ.apk" class="btn" download>
            📲 Baixar APK (32 MB)
        </a>
        
        <div class="version">
            ⚡ Dados salvos localmente | Atualizações gratuitas
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
